Privacy Policy
All Bangla Newspaper app is a free app. Any one can use it freely from anywhere.
If someone decides to use my services, this page is used to inform visitors about my policies with the collection, use, and disclosure of personal information.
If you choose to use my services, you consent to the collection and disclosure of personal information. Use the information regarding this policy. I shall not ask you to provide any personal information when using our services.
Information Collection and Use
I shall not ask you to provide any personal information when using our services.
Log Data
I would like to point out that whenever you use my service, in case of an error in the application, I will collect data and information (through third-party products) on your phone called Log Data. This log information may include your device's Internet Protocol ("IP") address, device name, operating system version, application configuration when using my Services, time and date of your use of the Services, and other statistics and other information.
Cookies
Cookies are files containing small pieces of information, often used as anonymous identifiers. This information is sent to your browser by the websites you visit and stored in your memory.
This service does not indicate the use of "cookies". However, the app will use third-party code and libraries that use "cookies" to collect information and improve its services. You can choose to accept or reject these cookies and know when a cookie is being sent to your device. If you choose not to accept our cookies you may not be able to use certain areas of the Service.
Security
As, I can’t request any personal information from you, our app is safe to use. But remember that, no app in the internet or any transmission medium or any method of electronic is 100% secure and reliable, and I cannot guarantee its absolute security.
Links to Other Sites
This Service may contain links to other sites. Links to external websites that may be found in our applications are for informational purposes only. Any information or statements that appeared in these sites or app are not sponsored, endorsed, or otherwise approved by All Bangla Newspaper. For these external sites, All Bangla Newspaper cannot be held liable for the availability of, or the content located on or through it. Also, any loss or damage arising from the use of the content or the Internet generally.
All content on the particular website is the property of that website. We have no rights over the content/logos of other websites. These third-party websites have separate privacy and content policies. Therefore, I strongly advise you to review the Privacy Policy of these websites. I have no control over and assume no responsibility for the content, privacy policies, or practices of any third-party sites or services.
Children’s Privacy
The Services are not directed to persons under the age of 13. I do not collect personal information from children under 13. If I discover that a child under the age of 13 has provided me with personal information, I will immediately remove the information from our servers.
Changes to This Privacy Policy
I may update our privacy policy from time to time. Therefore, it is recommended that you check this page regularly to see if there have been any changes. I will notify you of any changes by posting a new Privacy Policy on this page. This policy is valid as of December 15, 2023.
Contact Us
If you have any questions or suggestions about my Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact me at our email address “rummancste@gmail.com”
